Title: A Tester's Guide to Entering Zaralek
Description:
Hail, and well met!

While the story of Zaralek has yet to unfold, there is plenty to see within the cavern! Make way to Loamm, home of the Niffen.
ObjectivesText: Enter Zaralek Cavern through Iridikron's Gambit.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Fly through Iridikron's Gambit and meet Mimuup in Loamm.
